707369f-a.title: Brooklyn: Willoughby Ave. - Tompkins Ave.
707369f-a.text:
Willoughby Ave., north side, west from Tompkins Ave., showing
at the N.W. corner, the Tompkins Ave. M.E. Church, now a synagogue,
known as the Congregation Ohel Moshe Cheirathhelm.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
